### ============= STUDENTS CRUD ENDPOINTS (GUID) =============

### 4. Create Student (Direct)
POST http://localhost:5037/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nisn": "9876543210",
  "fullName": "Alice Johnson",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "AlicePass123!",
  "phoneNumber": "081234567892"
}

### 5. Get All Students
GET http://localhost:5037/api/students

### 6. Get Student by ID (Use GUID from Create response)
GET http://localhost:5037/api/students/{{student_guid_here}}

### 7. Get Student by NISN
GET http://localhost:5037/api/students/nisn/1234567890

### 8. Get Student by Email
GET http://localhost:5037/api/students/email/student@example.com

### 9. Update Student (Use GUID from Create response)
PUT http://localhost:5037/api/students/{{student_guid_here}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nisn": "1234567890",
  "fullName": "John Doe Updated",
  "email": "student.updated@example.com",
  "password": "NewPassword123!",
  "phoneNumber": "081234567899"
}

### 10. Delete Student (Use GUID from Create response)
DELETE http://localhost:5037/api/students/{{student_guid_here}}

